snippet: Steele completed an eight-under-par 64 in the morning and shot a 70 in the second round to take a three-stroke lead in the Texas Open in San Antonio.
abstract: Brendan Steele takes three-stroke lead at Texas Open in San Antonio; other golf news noted.
